---
---
<section id="equipe" class="bg-[oklch(97%_0.004_250)] px-6 py-20 md:px-12 md:py-[120px]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1240px]">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-16 md:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr]">
      <div data-aos="fade-right">
        <span class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-primary">Quem está por trás</span>
        <h2 class="mb-5 mt-3.5 font-display text-[28px] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)] md:text-[38px]">O que combinamos é o que você recebe.</h2>
        <p class="m-0 text-[15.5px] leading-[1.65] text-[oklch(42%_0.012_250)]">Sem letra miúda, sem "isso não estava incluso". Os dois fundadores acompanham o projeto do início ao fim — e garantem que o combinado sai do papel.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-[18px] border border-[oklch(90%_0.006_250)] bg-white p-2 shadow-[0_20px_40px_-24px_oklch(20%_0.02_250_/_0.15)]" data-aos="zoom-in">
          <div class="h-[220px] overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img src="/team/bernardo.jpeg" alt="Bernardo Dornelles" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-3 pb-2 pt-[18px]">
            <div class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)]">Bernardo Dornelles</div>
            <div class="mt-0.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-primary">Co-fundador</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[18px] border border-[oklch(90%_0.006_250)] bg-white p-2 shadow-[0_20px_40px_-24px_oklch(20%_0.02_250_/_0.15)] md:translate-y-5" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="120">
          <div class="h-[220px] overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img src="/team/selso.jpeg" alt="Selso Pacheco" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-3 pb-2 pt-[18px]">
            <div class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)]">Selso Pacheco</div>
            <div class="mt-0.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-primary">Co-fundador</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
